-opinion/.highlight/why-this-israeli-lawmaker-supported-south-africas-genocide-case-against-israel/0000018d-f795-dd0a-afcf-ffd7e2c20000</link><description>MK奥弗·卡西夫写道，关于他支持哈马斯针对以色列的武装斗争的指控是一个“公然、粗暴的谎言”，将他驱逐出议会的企图是为了“压制每一个批评的声音，特别是来自以色列的声音”。他所代表的国家的阿拉伯公民</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 02:02:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-01/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/why-this-israeli-lawmaker-supported-south-africas-genocide-case-against-israel/0000018d-f795-dd0a-afcf-ffd7e2c20000</guid></item></channel></rss>